    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/172658c4882265d59e66e1ff0a7302f4.avif?t=1770942300\" width=616 height=66 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/794a9a6e6f57b2d28f473c6fa7f8e499.webp?t=1770942300\" width=616 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;<i>Karoshi Club</i>&quot; is a first-person horror adventure game. Take on the role of <i>Kumi Yamane</i>, a driven career young woman and highly successful manager in the soul sales industry.  The afterlife world of Yomi is on a significant major upheaval, and the Keneō Industry сorporation will be the first to suffer from the impending disaster. Navigate a complex web of mysteries, make crucial decisions, and try to survive in a world you have helped change. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/10f66a6dafcdd12acc548ad57f470b0b.poster.avif?t=1770942300\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/10f66a6dafcdd12acc548ad57f470b0b.webm?t=1770942300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/10f66a6dafcdd12acc548ad57f470b0b.mp4?t=1770942300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/f8bbd0e2f02a8d1a936fe2513f005ccb.avif?t=1770942300\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i><strong>Sales Manager Simulator: </strong></i><strong>During work hours, sell souls over the phone, sing karaoke after work… and eat the most disgusting ramen of your afterlife.</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>Dark Japanese Business Punk:</i> Imagine the afterlife world of Yomi from Japanese medieval myth, but in modern times with modern issues, empty offices, and a realm full of ghosts.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>Horror Manga Visual Style:</i> We combined 3D technology with 2D character images to create an immersive interactive manga feeling.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/958f2f4bed82887034f7925251cf99d3.avif?t=1770942300\" width=616 height=122 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/210f6d0fa9b327a21ee61a6ba5dea1e3.avif?t=1770942300\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">- Moshi Moshi<br>- You will get a job in Seven Days </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/2c82342a7e266c3469f4c210f95837e5.avif?t=1770942300\" width=616 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Our multinational indie team is a group of game developers impacted by layoffs in the gaming industry in 2023. However, we refused to give up and used this to create something of our own. We are determined to develop games and create specific worlds we are passionate about, and we hope you will love them just as much as we do. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen to the stories from Kamishibai while you sit back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/0d85b3327733836d98430e77577334dc.webp?t=1770942300\" width=616 height=44 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218870/extras/529f0406ac684a658aafc60a5fc75682.avif?t=1770942300\" width=616 height=134 /></span></p>",
